map works again, fix in commit comment

to fix due to local.props loss: 

1. add 
GOOGLEMAPS_APIKEY = xxxxx 
to local.properties

2. add 
resValue "string", "GOOGLEMAPS_API_KEY", "\"${getProperty("local.properties", "GOOGLEMAPS_APIKEY")}\"" 
to app level build.gradle under defaultConfig{

3. add <meta-data
            android:name="com.google.android.maps.v2.API_KEY"
                android:value="@string/GOOGLEMAPS_API_KEY"
                />
to AndroidManifest under <application
fixed the item count and added on click listener
